# SegmentKey Inequality operator

Tests two segment keys for inequality.

```csharp
public static bool operator !=(SegmentKey left, SegmentKey right)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| left | The first segment key. |
| right | The second segment key. |

## Return Value

Returns `true` if the segment keys are not equal; `false` otherwise.
